import React from "react";
import { Center, Box, Heading, Grid } from "@chakra-ui/react";

export const Reactions: React.FC = () => {
  return (
    <Box h={"100vh"}>
      <Center h={"100%"}>
        <Grid h={10} templateColumns="repeat(5, 1fr)" gap={6}>
          <Box w="100px" h="10" textAlign="center">
            <Heading>😡</Heading>
          </Box>
          <Box w="100px" h="10" textAlign="center">
            <Heading>😕</Heading>
          </Box>
          <Box w="100px" h="10" textAlign="center">
            <Heading>😶</Heading>
          </Box>
          <Box w="100px" h="10" textAlign="center">
            <Heading>😁</Heading>
          </Box>
          <Box w="100px" h="10" textAlign="center">
            <Heading>😍</Heading>
          </Box>
        </Grid>
      </Center>
    </Box>
  );
};
